OK, here's how it works. First,buff and sow your self. Then snare 3 to 4 mobs. Circle strafe around them until they are so close together they look like 1 mob. Then kite them with Lightning Strike.<br>
<br>
Now, as to what and where? I'll answer that as best I can (meaning what Ive done). First, go to Tiz 1. This is the northermost tizmak cave in Great Divide. You want to snare the two outside the cave, and the one that pops on the hill to the north. Quad-kite (Tri-kite actually) these until they start to green out. Then go to the Tower of Frozen Shadow. Quad kite the Shadow Guardians around the base of the tower. After these begin to get green, you can move on to dire wolves near the EW bridge. That is where I am now.<br>
<br>
